snippet.title: Homicipher - Official Chapter One Update Announcement Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description: Watch the latest trailer for the text-based adventure horror game Homicipher. Solve intricate puzzles and ciphers to uncover a thrilling narrative revolving around a series of gruesome murders, testing your wits and deductive skills. The free Chapter One update for Homicipher is launching in the second half of 2023.
